{"id":"30962","title":"冷宫公主种田记","writer":"金夭夭","dateline":"1442898894","updatetime":"1442898894","isover":"1","filesize":"7456066","linecount":"43469","wordcount":"2440142","imgpath":"https://photos.smugmug.com/photos/i-zFRkK7C/0/f559549d/Th/i-zFRkK7C-Th.jpg","hash":"lenggonggongzhuzhongtianji","urlhash":"","sign":"","desc":"小说阅读网VIP2015-04-07完结\n文案\n投胎成冷宫公主，一出生就被丢到了宫外，以为穿越能来享福，谁知道还是来到了一穷二白的穷人家，沈思思欲哭无泪，好在有了随身空间，空间在手，吃喝不愁，她努力奋斗，凭着智慧和空间带着家人发家致富，当终于让吉祥三兄弟出人头地，养成成功能挑一个顺利嫁了时……宫里却找到了她，要逼着她去和番邦的小王爷和亲，听说那王爷是个断袖，听说他是个残暴，听说他……只爱平胸男，不爱美人女……听说……好吧，王爷，咱打个商量行吗？你玩你的断袖，我玩我的种田，代价是顺便提供美食和帮他管家。哪知王爷却吃上了瘾，他眯着邪眸，坏笑道：“本王既爱美食，但更爱美女啊，尤其是公主这样的绝色美女……”但面对他后院里的众多美男，沈思思头痛，这个王妃……不好当。","hot":"0","num":"0","cid":"169","suggcate":"穿越重生","suggcids":"169,166","notbook":"0","fetchv":"0","lasthot":"0","clicknum":"69","isvip":"1","ish":"0","age":"现代","channel":"女","isqiniu":"1","list":"0,2yv,661,902,cf7,ftt,j0o,lys,oxl,ssz,vq1,ylp,11qx,155s,186d,1at5,1el7,1htc,1l1d,1oha,1s2j,1vo9,1yn3,223g,25mq,287v,2bci,2eon,2ics,2lem,2osu,2rvd,2uzb,2y4g,31id,34yq,38i1,3br3,3f6e,3ifj,3lvz,3p56,3sq2,3w53,40kl,4413,47ra,4bfl,4edf,4h2z,4ki2,4ncm,4qjd,4tya,4xmi,518v,54iw,57s2,5bn6,5eoi,5huv,5ldp,5oto,5s43,5wen,5zrv,62z3,66dy,690e,6ca4,6f96,6iwb,6n4c,6qrw,6uao,6ybh,71ll,74td,787b,7bh5,7fi7,7izh,7m0b,7pc8,7spp,7w6d,800p,83vb,87mb,8b7w,8e7l,8h0f,8l9c,8o1q,8rac,8v2z,8yjw,91dh,94sc,97q7,9bhq,9f5e,9iw8,9msa,9qm7,9u4d,9wvx,a0a7,a3o8,a6hw,a99h,acn5,afe7,aid6,alg1,ao8g,arna,aumx,axek,b0dp,b3gz,b634,b98w,bcif,bfe5,bi62,bm8m,bpca,brxp,burb,bxes,c076,c335,c5ls,c936,cc08,cf0x,chrb,ckoq,cn9q,cqde,ctip,cwnk,d0ej,d3e6,d6jy,d9ok,dci1,dfa2,dipp,dlfl,do7x,dqtk,dtj2,dw8e,dzeq,e23x,e50s,e7tw,eane,edgl,eg0j,ej2j,em3l,epnf,es8b,evn9,eygm,f126,f3yi,f6ur,f9hr,fc9t,fftv,fj7f,fm0u,fpp2,fta4,fwdk,fzfc,g2pl,g587,g933,gc4j,gf61,gij2,gm6z,gps4,gthx,gwsn,gz96,h2k6,h5yr,ha4a,hdby,hg7g,hjml,hmm5,hpog,hswn,hw8v,hzle,i34t,i6rj,ia79,idom,ih93,ikll,inzc,ir86,iuw5,iyul,j24j,j5kt,j8w6,jcer,jf11,jhwa,jkhk,jnd2,jpx7,jtjy,jww3,k0sy,k3oz,k6ja,k9i4,kcuh,kg4t,kjry,kne0